{
  "texts": [
    "Examples of environmental monitoring include: (a) Energy consumption monitoring: Assessing the AI system's energy usage and identifying opportunities for optimization.",
    "(b) Carbon footprint monitoring: Evaluating the AI system's greenhouse gas emissions and implementing strategies to reduce its environmental impact.",
    "(c) Ecosystem impact monitoring: Examining the AI system's effects on ecosystems, such as habitat disruption or biodiversity loss, and devising mitigation measures.",
    "Temporal monitoring(a) Slow monitoring: Periodic evaluation of the AI system's behavior and performance over an extended timeframe.",
    "(b) Live monitoring: Real-time tracking and assessment of the AI system's operation to detect and address potential issues immediately.6."
  ]
}